---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"plan\"])"
---
Interactive spec interview (`-n <label>` new, `-u <label>` update)

Usage: loom plan [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -n <LABEL>               New-spec interview for `<label>`
  -w, --workspace <PATH>   Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>    Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi]
  -u <LABEL>               Update-spec interview for `<label>`
      --profile <PROFILE>  Override the profile resolution chain. Wins over `[phase.plan].profile` and `[phase.default].profile` in `<workspace>/config.toml` (default `base`)
  -h, --help               Print help
